  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TCP报文结构的示意图，用来做工业物联网MQTT通信的教学。重点是把头部那些控制位和端口信息展示清楚。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "TCP Packet Structure",
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，TCP头部前32位是源端口和目标端口对吧？然后序列号和确认号各占32位，这个顺序我理解没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Sequence Number",
        "Acknowledgment Number"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。接下来96到111位是控制位区域，URG、ACK、PSH、RST、SYN、FIN这六个标志位各占1位，这个顺序是标准定义不能改。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "URG",
        "ACK",
        "PSH",
        "RST",
        "SYN",
        "FIN",
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我已经把控制位区域画好了。然后112到127位是Window窗口大小，128到143是Checksum校验和，144到159是Urgent Pointer紧急指针，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Window",
        "Checksum",
        "Urgent Pointer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对的。不过我们这是面向工业物联网的场景，160到191位我想标注成IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker，表示这个字段在实际部署中可能被用于承载MQTT代理相关的扩展信息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，160-191位标记为IoT_Industrial_MQTT_Broker。最后192到255位就是Data数据载荷部分了，这样整个头部结构就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，确认一下，Data Offset和Reserved加起来是10位对吧？96-99是4位的Data Offset，100-105是6位的Reserved，我之前说的控制位从106开始没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data Offset",
        "Reserved",
        "URG"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认无误，106位开始是URG，整个结构我已经检查过了，所有字段的位宽和顺序都符合标准TCP头部定义，加上IoT扩展标注，现在可以定稿了。",
